
[1] - or d 
  If it is a file, then -; if it is directory, then d

Group[2-4]or[5-7]or[8-10]
r: read
w: write
x: execute

Group1: permission for the owner
Group2: permission for the group
Group3: permission for anyone else

u - user
g - group
o - others

chmod o+w filename   #Give others write permission
chmod o-w filename   #Take the permission away

---------------------
chmod 754 filenmae
4 - read
2 - write
1 - execute
0 - no permission

